---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Work With Me">
  <article class="container section">
    <h1 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">Work With Me</h1>

    <div style="max-width: 65ch; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-xl);">
      <section>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md);">I manufacture and distribute good ideas.</h2>
        <p>I'm interested in interesting problems. If you're building something, stuck on something, or just have an idea worth thinking through — this is where that starts.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">Some conversations turn into engagements. Some turn into something neither of us expected. A few just sharpen the thinking. All of them are worth having.</p>
        <p style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">Tell me what you're working on.</p>
      </section>

      <section style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
        <form action="#" method="POST" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-lg); max-width: 600px;">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="label" style="display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required class="form-input" style="width: 100%;" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="email" class="label" style="display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required class="form-input" style="width: 100%;" />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="message" class="label" style="display: block; margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);">Message</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message" required class="form-input" rows="6" placeholder="What are you working on?" style="width: 100%; resize: vertical; font-family: var(--font-mono);"></textarea>
          </div>

          <button type="submit" class="btn btn--accent">Start a Conversation</button>
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
